{
  "stem": "21812.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I sort of felt the-- the arrogance of the Austrians, what I perceived as arrogance, and also felt that nothing really had changed, that 50% were Socialists and 50% were still Nazis.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we looked at the sites, and I said I would never go back again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I might have to go back again next year, because my daughter-in-law's father was an architect.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He wants me to give him a tour after going to Milan, and give him a tour of Vienna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I don't know if-- I might have to do it, but I'm not particularly-- you know, I have no feelings for it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to my grandmother's house, which is still there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went to my own house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't go upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's now locked downstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can't walk in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You have to have a key.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first time I-- as I said, I-- well, you know, I had strange feelings about being back here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yet they were more in terms of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] of relationships that were sort of-- I felt like somebody who has Alzheimer's.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some things were still in the same place, and others weren't, and some were much larger, seemed larger, and some smaller.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was very disoriented.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I felt very strange in that respect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had seen it as a child, and now I'm coming back and-- but the second time I think-- as I said, I went there the first time, I really wanted to just not think about that and just have a good time.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the second time I, for instance, went back into the school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the school was open.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was open because they were voting and, like here, they keep the schools open.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
